---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Mobile App Development Services | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Professional mobile app development services for iOS, Android, and cross-platform solutions in the UAE."
  path="/services/mobile-apps/"
>

  <section class="service-content" id="mobile-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2>Mobile App Development Services</h2>
      <p>We craft innovative mobile applications that deliver exceptional user experiences across all devices and platforms. Our team of experts combines creative design with technical excellence to build apps that users love and businesses rely on.</p>

      <h3>Native iOS Development</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>iPhone Apps</h4><p>Beautiful, high-performance iOS apps built with Swift and SwiftUI following Apple's Human Interface Guidelines.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>iPad Apps</h4><p>Optimized iPad experiences with multitasking, split view, and Apple Pencil support.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Apple Watch Apps</h4><p>Wearable experiences that extend your iOS app with complications, notifications, and health tracking.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>App Store Optimization</h4><p>Expert guidance on App Store submission, optimization, and download growth strategies.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Native Android Development</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Kotlin Development:</strong> Modern, concise Android apps using Kotlin and Jetpack Compose</li>
        <li><strong>Material Design:</strong> Beautiful interfaces following Google's Material Design 3 guidelines</li>
        <li><strong>Tablet Optimization:</strong> Responsive layouts that adapt to different screen sizes and foldables</li>
        <li><strong>Wear OS Apps:</strong> Smartwatch applications for Android wearable devices</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Cross-Platform Development</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>React Native</h4><p>Build once, deploy on iOS and Android with native performance using React Native and JavaScript.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Flutter</h4><p>Beautiful natively compiled apps with Flutter's rich widget library and hot reload.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Progressive Web Apps</h4><p>Web applications that behave like native apps with offline support, notifications, and home screen installation.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Cost-Effective Solutions</h4><p>Reduce development time and cost by maintaining a single codebase for multiple platforms.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Types of Mobile Apps We Build</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>E-commerce Apps:</strong> Shopping apps with product catalogs, cart, payment integration, and order tracking</li>
        <li><strong>Social Networking:</strong> Community platforms with messaging, feeds, profiles, and content sharing</li>
        <li><strong>On-Demand Services:</strong> Uber-like apps for ride-sharing, food delivery, and service marketplaces</li>
        <li><strong>Healthcare Apps:</strong> Telemedicine, fitness tracking, appointment booking, and health monitoring</li>
        <li><strong>Education Apps:</strong> E-learning platforms, course delivery, quizzes, and progress tracking</li>
        <li><strong>Finance & Banking:</strong> Mobile banking, payment apps, and investment platforms</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Mobile App Security</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Secure Authentication:</strong> Biometric authentication, OAuth 2.0, JWT tokens, and MFA</li>
        <li><strong>Data Encryption:</strong> End-to-end encryption for sensitive data</li>
        <li><strong>API Security:</strong> Secure communication with SSL pinning and request signing</li>
        <li><strong>Secure Storage:</strong> Encrypted local storage using Keychain (iOS) and KeyStore (Android)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Our Mobile Tech Stack</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>iOS:</strong> Swift, SwiftUI, UIKit, Combine, Core Data, CloudKit</li>
        <li><strong>Android:</strong> Kotlin, Jetpack Compose, Android SDK, Room, WorkManager</li>
        <li><strong>Cross-Platform:</strong> React Native, Flutter, Dart, JavaScript/TypeScript</li>
        <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Firebase, AWS Amplify, GraphQL, REST APIs</li>
        <li><strong>Design:</strong> Figma, Sketch, Adobe XD</li>
        <li><strong>Testing:</strong> XCTest, Espresso, Jest, Detox, Appium</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container"><div class="contact-content">
      <h2>Let's Build Something Great Together</h2>
      <p>Ready to transform your business with cutting-edge technology solutions? Get in touch with our team today.</p>
      <div class="contact-info">
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><a href="/contact/"><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong><br>Get in touch</a></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span></div>
      </div>
    </div></div>
  </section>

</Layout>
